-- German Lawmaker Pfeiffer Wants Energy Subsidy Cut, Handelsblatt Reports
-- B y   C h r i s t i a n   V i t s
-- 2010-12-07T07:21:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-07/germany-s-pfeiffer-wants-energy-subsidy-cut-handelsblatt-says.html
Germany should consider cutting its
aid for renewable energy, Christian Democrat lawmaker  Joachim Pfeiffer  said,  Handelsblatt  reported, citing an interview.  The development of subsidies for renewable energy is
“worrisome,” the CDU parliamentary spokesman for economy and
energy was quoted as  saying . Pfeiffer is in particular focusing
on aid cuts in the solar industry, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Christian Vits  in Frankfurt at 
 cvits@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
